# ============================================================================
# Flight Rescheduler - Environment Variables Template
# ============================================================================
# 
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. For Convex deployment: Add these to Convex Dashboard
#    https://dashboard.convex.dev → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#
# 2. For local .env file: Copy this to `.env` and fill in your keys
# ============================================================================

# ===== REQUIRED: Weather API =====
# Get your free API key from: https://openweathermap.org/api
# Free tier: 1,000 calls/day (sufficient with caching)
OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_openweather_api_key_here

# ===== REQUIRED: AI Provider (Choose ONE) =====

# Option 1: OpenAI (Recommended - GPT-4o-mini)
# Get key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Cost: ~$0.15 per 1M input tokens, ~$0.60 per 1M output tokens
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Option 2: Anthropic (Claude 3.5 Sonnet)
# Get key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
# Cost: ~$3 per 1M input tokens, ~$15 per 1M output tokens
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here

# Note: You only need ONE AI provider key
# System uses OpenAI by default if both are provided

# ===== OPTIONAL: Alternative Weather API =====
# If using WeatherAPI.com instead of OpenWeatherMap
# Get key from: https://www.weatherapi.com/
# WEATHERAPI_KEY=your_weatherapi_key_here

# ===== OPTIONAL: Custom API Endpoints =====
# Only needed for custom/proxied endpoints
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com

# ===== SETUP STEPS =====
#
# For Convex Deployment (Recommended):
# 1. Go to https://dashboard.convex.dev
# 2. Select your project → Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Add each variable with your actual API keys
# 4. Deploy: `npx convex deploy`
#
# For Local Development:
# 1. Copy this file: `cp env.example .env`
# 2. Edit `.env` and add your real API keys
# 3. The `.env` file is gitignored for security
#
# ===== SECURITY NOTES =====
# ⚠️  NEVER commit .env files with real keys to git
# ⚠️  Keep API keys secret and rotate if exposed
# ⚠️  Use separate keys for dev and production
#
# ===== COST ESTIMATES =====
# OpenWeatherMap: FREE (1,000 calls/day)
#   With caching: ~50-100 actual calls/day
#
# OpenAI GPT-4o-mini: ~$0.0002 per reschedule
#   (Very affordable - 2 cents per 100 reschedules)
#
# Anthropic Claude: ~$0.002 per reschedule
#   (Higher quality - 20 cents per 100 reschedules)
#
# Convex: FREE tier sufficient for dev + small production
#   (1M function calls/month, 1GB storage)
